name: NODEJS Kotori
tagline: A simple and open-source Discord Bot for your server.
body:
### Features.
NODEJS Kotori can perform simple administrative commands and a few extra things. she can even gather the latest news!

### Adding to your Discord server.
I have made adding the bot to your server easier using suckybots by abal.
+ for stable : http://suckybots.abal.moe/bots/189963740031090688
+ for Cutting Edge (Unstable) :http://suckybots.abal.moe/bots/189964084597227523

### Contributing.
it's easy to contribute! just pull up a Pull Request on daily and I (or we,soon?) will review what changes you made.
We won't bite! plus we won't scold you from your bad coding :) .
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
